}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This device may have an alternative model of RNWD-11008.
"0236B", "ROHS", and a date code of '''1202''' (presumably Jan. 2012) is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. No external FE/PA modules are visible. :This would appear to be a '''[[Zioncom]]''' WL0236 / WL0236B.
The USB ID for this device is presumed to be the default RT5572 ID (148f:5572).
